'''''Venom 2''''' is an upcoming film based on the Marvel Comics [[Venom|character of the same name]]. It will be the sequel to ''[[Venom (film)|Venom]]'' and the third film of the proposed [[Sony's Universe of Marvel Characters]]. == Premise == == Cast == *[[Tom Hardy]] as [[Venom|Eddie Brock/Venom]] *[[Michelle Williams]] as [[Anne Weying]] *[[Reid Scott]] as [[Dr. Dan Lewis]] *[[Woody Harrelson]] as [[Carnage|Cletus Kasady/Carnage]] *[[w:c:MCU:Tom Holland|Tom Holland]] as [[w:c:MCU:Spider-Man|Peter Parker/Spider-Man]] == Production == Venom 2 will begin filming on November 25, 2019. == External links == *''[[Wikipedia:Venom 2|Venom 2]]'' on ''Wikipedia'' {| class="article-table" style="width:100%;" role="complementary" |- style="font-size:18px;" ! style="padding:0px;" |
